@OrderManagement_HostAddress = http://localhost:5263

### Get all orders
GET {{OrderManagement_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Accept: application/json

### Get order by ID (replace with actual GUID)
GET {{OrderManagement_HostAddress}}/api/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

### Create new order
POST {{OrderManagement_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderNumber": "ORD-001",
  "customerName": "John Doe",
  "customerEmail": "john.doe@example.com",
  "totalAmount": 150.00,
  "shippingAddress": "123 Main St, City, Country",
  "description": "Sample order"
}

### Update order (replace with actual GUID)
PUT {{OrderManagement_HostAddress}}/api/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "John Updated",
  "status": 2,
  "totalAmount": 175.00
}

### Delete order (replace with actual GUID)
DELETE {{OrderManagement_HostAddress}}/api/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Get orders by status (0=Pending, 1=Confirmed, 2=Processing, 3=Shipped, 4=Delivered, 5=Cancelled)
GET {{OrderManagement_HostAddress}}/api/orders/status/0
Accept: application/json

### Get orders by customer name
GET {{OrderManagement_HostAddress}}/api/orders/customer/John
Accept: application/json

